
Getting started
===============

    $ cd strace
    $ autoconf
    $ make

     - src/tests-sbox      : test codes
          /sbox.{c,h}      : system call hooks
          /strace.c        : main

    $ ./strace -h          : help
    $ ./strace ls          : run ls with ptrace
    $ ./strace -s ls       : run ls with seccomp/bpf
    $ ./strace -i sh       : run sh (interactive mode after you kill the sh)
    $ ./testall.sh         : test all unit tests

    # examples
    $ ./strace -i -- wget google.com      : a simple use
    $ ./strace -n -i -- wget google.com   : no network
    
NOTE. Python: the orignal PoC
-----------------------------

    $ cd src
    $ make libseccomp.so

     - src/sandbox.py      : main ptrace wrapper
          /spec.py         : definition of syscalls
          /{util,dbg}.py   : helper functions
          /tests/test-*    : test codes

    $ src/sandbox.py [opts] -- prog [args]
    $ src/sandbox.py -h
    $ src/sandbox.py -q -- python2 -i
